<br />
<br />I took a look at your ADPCM codec.. pretty cool, though I want to try to keep things as high quality as possible (ie no compression).  plus i'm not sure how exactly to encode files into that format lol.  as for reducing bitrate on the fly with the nes, the results would be less than satisfactory.  I prefer to do all the bitrate conversion in a wave editor and use more advanced dithering algorithms  than simple bit shifting.</div>

